  "prompt": "Is there any good institute for differently abled child near Noida areas?",
  "response": "Yes, there are several institutes and organizations in and around Noida that cater to the needs of differently abled children. Here are a few you might consider:\n\n1. **Shiksha Niketan** - An institution that focuses on inclusive education for children with special needs.\n\n2. **The Miracle School** - Located in Noida, this school provides education and therapy for children with various disabilities.\n\n3. **Manasvini** - A special school in Noida that offers education and therapy for children with intellectual and developmental disabilities.\n\n4. **Aastha - The Confidence School** - This school is dedicated to students with learning disabilities, providing special education and support.\n\n5. **Sankalp School** - Located in Noida, Sankalp provides individualized education and therapy for children with special needs.\n\n6. **Special Olympics Bharat - Noida Chapter** - While primarily focused on sports, they also support various initiatives for children with disabilities.\n\nIt's important to visit the schools and speak with faculty to find the best fit for your child's needs. You can also check reviews and speak with other parents for recommendations.",
